  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ\u2019s tax-inclusive pricing feature is tailored for businesses operating in regions where local legislation mandates managing and displaying prices, including taxes. This ensures a seamless and transparent pricing experience for customers.</p><p>In markets like Australia, where Goods and Services Tax (GST) applies, RepairQ can be configured to manage tax-inclusive pricing in compliance with regulations. This feature ensures that unit pricing, discounts, and ticket totals include tax, while accurately calculating the base price for gross profit analysis and providing a detailed tax breakdown for customer invoicing and accounting.</p><p>Key Features:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Catalog Price Including Tax</strong> - The catalog will convert the unit price to \u2018price including tax\u2019. This will enable users to enter and manage a single catalog unit price including tax.  </p></li><li><p><strong>Price and Tax Breakdown</strong> - RepairQ automatically calculates the base price and tax breakdown for invoicing and reporting of gross profits. </p></li><li><p><strong>Discount Management </strong>- Discounts, whether fixed prices or percentages can be applied, including tax. </p></li><li><p><strong>Customer Invoices &amp; Receipts</strong> - Customer paperwork can be configured to show tax-inclusive pricing and tax paid per unit.  </p></li><li><p><strong>Display Layout </strong>- Configure default labels for price, including tax, across key features such as tickets and lists.</p></li></ul><p>Our resources provide instructions for converting a location to tax-inclusive pricing.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1986560223/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricingResources-Tax-InclusiveSetup\">Tax-Inclusive Setup</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1984823420\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: Company and Location Setup</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933410332\" rel=\"nofollow\">Setting up and Assigning Tax Rates</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1986035723\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: Customize Ticket Display</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1986560182\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: GST Invoice Template</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2713288722\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing: GST Receipt Template</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"Tax-inclusivePricingResources-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932394639\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tax-inclusive Pricing on Tickets</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932329061\" rel=\"nofollow\">Create a Catalog Item</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2717712385\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cash Transaction Currency Settings</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2713124902\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cash Rounding Options</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934196764\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Taxes</a></p></li></ul><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
